2US%20solar%20producers%20could%20finally%20have%20a%20fighting%20chance%20as%20tariffs%20kick%20in%20on%20cheaper%20imports%20from%20Asia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20engineers%20bring%20the%20solar%20panel%20for%20installation%20at%20the%20solar%20farm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6661fce51cd3b17790440a66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESutthichai%20Supapornpasupad%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETariffs%20are%20back%20on%20cheap%20solar%20products%20coming%20from%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20duties%20were%20paused%20to%20ensure%20US%20access%20to%20solar%2C%20but%20caused%20a%20supply%20glut.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20tariff%20holiday%20over%2C%20domestic%20producers%20stand%20to%20benefit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20are%20finally%20in%20play%20on%20cheap%20solar%20imports%20from%20Asia%20after%20a%20two-year%20moratorium%20on%20the%20restrictions%20expired%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20renewal%20of%20these%20taxes%2C%20which%20target%20Chinese-affiliated%20solar%20products%20exported%20from%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20is%20an%20early%20step%20in%20leveling%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20US%20manufacturers%2C%20one%20analyst%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20moratorium%20should%20ease%20price%20volatility%2C%20bringing%20%26quot%3Ba%20level%20of%20stability%20to%20the%20marketplace%20that%2C%20frankly%2C%20it's%20good%20for%20developers%2C%20it's%20good%20for%20producers%2C%20it's%20good%20for%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Carr%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Solar%20Energy%20Manufacturers%20of%20America%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitecase.com%2Finsight-alert%2Fus-department-commerce-determines-imports-southeast-asia-are-circumventing-addcvd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetermined%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Chinese%20solar%20was%20making%20its%20way%20into%20the%20US%20duty-free%2C%20despite%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20the%20country.%20Instead%2C%20Chinese%20producers%20would%20route%20their%20modules%20through%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20which%20traded%20freely%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20close%20the%20loophole%2C%20the%20department%20issued%20tariffs%20on%20these%20regions%20as%20well.%20But%20their%20impact%20has%20never%20been%20felt%2C%20given%20a%20pre-emptive%20pause%20on%20the%20legislation%2C%20which%20just%20expired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20tariff%20moratorium%20were%20White%20House%20concerns%20that%20the%20restrictions%20could%20hinder%20US%20energy%20transition%2C%20as%20domestic%20solar%20production%20was%20still%20nascent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20gave%20way%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20cheap%20imports%2C%20causing%20solar%20prices%20to%20crater%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Carr's%20telling%2C%20that's%20because%20Southeast%20Asian%20producers%20never%20stopped%20manufacturing%20despite%20pausing%20trade%20during%20the%20department's%20investigation.%20Once%20the%20pause%20on%20tariffs%20took%20effect%2C%20the%20region%20unloaded%2C%20causing%20the%20massive%20supply%20glut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20level%20of%20imports%20far%20exceeded%20what%20was%20happening%20before%20the%20moratorium%20was%20put%20in%20place%2C%20and%20it%20just%20absolutely%20flooded%20our%20markets%20as%20well%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Carr%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20when%20that%20happened%2C%20that%20created%20just%20massive%20uncertainty%20around%20pricing%20going%20forward%20in%20our%20market%2C%20as%20prices%20continued%20to%20fall.%20And%20so%20it%20did%20have%20an%20effect%20of%20killing%20some%20of%20the%20investment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20extreme%2C%20the%20oversupply%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsolar-panel-price-cut-oversupply-us-renewable-energy-market-demand-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20panels%20cause%20global%20pricing%20to%20drop%20by%20half%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20with%20China%20driving%20the%20flood%20of%20supply.%20Meanwhile%2C%20solar%20shipments%20from%20Southeast%20Asian%20producers%20have%20not%20slowed%2C%20and%20accounted%20for%2087.5%25%20of%20US%20module%20imports%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spglobal.com%2Fmarketintelligence%2Fen%2Fnews-insights%2Flatest-news-headlines%2Fus-solar-panel-imports-near-record-levels-as-trade-probe-proceeds-81835205%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20could%20eventually%20bring%20upside%20for%20US%20producers%2C%20and%20Carr%20indicates%20that%20a%2025%25-30%25%20price%20correction%20for%20solar%20modules%20could%20materialize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20emphasized%20that%20pricing%20isn't%20a%20leading%20driver%20of%20solar%20deployment%2C%20and%20analysts%20should%20not%20focus%20too%20much%20on%20prices%20to%20measure%20the%20industry's%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20tariffs%20could%20succeed%20in%20calming%20volatility%20in%20the%20market%20and%20bringing%20back%20needed%20investment%20in%20the%20space%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20are%20other%20positives%20for%20the%20domestic%20industry%20to%20look%20forward%20to%2C%20David%20Feldman%20of%20the%20National%20Renewable%20Energy%20Laboratory%20told%20BI.%20The%20market%20could%20soon%20see%20further%20guidance%20on%20tax%20credits%20related%20to%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20and%20trade%20adjustments%20to%20boost%20US%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20the%20moratorium%20was%20lifted%20on%20Thursday%2C%20two%20major%20Chinese%20solar%20companies%20announced%20suspensions%20in