nable%20option%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20tips%20for%20kids'%20consignment%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247f312ab-7d10-4952-9ead-28a8fec89365%5C%22%3EI%20buy%20online%20and%20at%20consignment%20sales%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKidizen%20is%20the%20kids'%20equivalent%20of%20the%20popular%20consignment%20site%20Poshmark.%20I%20use%20it%20for%20buying%20as%20it's%20easy%20to%20filter%20by%20brand%2C%20size%2C%20and%20item%20quality%2C%20and%20shipping%20is%20fairly%20inexpensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20great%20local%20consignment%20sales%20where%20I%20live%20in%20Raleigh%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20many%20of%20which%20happen%20twice%20a%20year%20(in%20early%20fall%20and%20early%20spring).%20They're%20great%20for%20buying%20many%20items%20at%20once%20and%20for%20building%20out%20my%20kids'%20closet%20for%20the%20upcoming%20season.%20These%20sales%20are%20typically%20only%20a%20few%20days%20long%2C%20and%20on%20the%20last%20day%2C%20items%20are%20usually%20reduced%20even%20further%20for%20mega%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChances%20are%20there%20are%20similar%20sales%20or%20consignment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fbest-kids-clothes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estores%20specifically%20for%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20your%20area.%20If%20you're%20not%20familiar%20with%20any%2C%20ask%20your%20local%20parenting%20group%20or%20do%20a%20quick%20Google%20search%20to%20find%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20is%20also%20a%20great%20place%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclothing-resale-popular-with-retailers-gen-z-sustainable-shoppers-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20kids'%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20find%20what%20you%20want%2C%20look%20for%20specific%20Buy%2FSell%2FTrade%20(BST)%20groups%20for%20brands%20you%20love%2C%20like%20the%20popular%20Mini%20Boden%20%26amp%3B%20Hanna%20Andersson%20BST%20group%20(wh