ing%20through%20the%20local%20seasonal%20consignment%20sales%20because%20they%20can%20take%20up%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20profit%20for%20each%20sale.%20They're%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-thrift-stores-worse-secondhand-clothing-market-popular-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20way%20to%20sell%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20quickly%2C%20though%2C%20so%20I'll%20take%20whatever%20hasn't%20sold%20through%20other%20methods%20to%20these%20and%20then%20donate%20whatever%20is%20leftover%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee1b3139-3748-45e1-9713-2943840fef31%5C%22%3ECertain%20brands%20have%20a%20higher%20resale%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-turn-resale-side-hustle-into-full-time-business-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresale%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20adult%20resale%20market.%20Higher-end%20brands%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20at%20reselling%2C%20and%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20more%20of%20your%20purchase%20price%20back%20when%20you%20resell%20them.%20Keep%20this%20in%20mind%20when%20you're%20buying%20(new%20or%20secondhand)%2C%20as%20the%20ability%20to%20resell%20effectively%20brings%20your%20purchase%20price%20down%20since%20you're%20making%20back%20some%20of%20what%20you%20spent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMass-market%20brands%20like%20Old%20Navy%20and%20Carters%20are%20tougher%20to%20resell%2C%20and%20you'll%20likely%20only%20be%20able%20to%20recoup%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20what%20you%20originally%20paid.%20Higher-end%20brands%20like%20Hanna%20Andersson%2C%20Mini%20Boden%2C%20and%20The%20Beaufort%20Bonnet%20Company%20have%20high%20resale%20values%20and%20often%20pass%20through%20several%20rounds%20of%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20buy%20an%20item%20from%20one%20of%20these%20brands%20secondhand%2C%20I%20can%20usually%20resell%20it%20for%2070-80%25%20of%20w