yone%20is%20telling%20me%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20that%20I%20have%20a%20bad%20habit%2C%20I%20want%20to%20fix%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20your%20friends%20say%20you're%20cheap.%20That%20answers%20the%20first%20question.%20Is%20everyone%20saying%20the%20same%20thing%3F%20Yes.%20That%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20second%20question%3A%20Is%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudgeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20hobby%20hurting%20other%20people%20more%20than%20it%20is%20helping%20you%3F%20You%20answered%20this%20question%20in%20your%20letter%20when%20you%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20make%20my%20penny-pinching%20ways%20their%20problem.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20examining%20this%20assertion%20before%20disregarding%20the%20collective%20criticism%20you're%20receiving%20from%20your%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20friend%20who%20reminds%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20you.%20We've%20been%20close%20since%20we%20were%20kids%2C%20and%20over%20the%20years%2C%20her%20money-loving%20personality%20has%20affected%20me%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20from%20mild%20irritation%20to%20real%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20non-comprehensive%20list%3A%20strong-arming%20me%20into%20splitting%20an%20entr%C3%A9e%3B%20embarrassing%20me%20by%20going%20over%20the%20finer%20details%20of%20expired%20coupons%20with%20shopkeepers%20and%20restaurant%20wait%20staff%3B%20making%20me%20wait%20in%20line%20with%20her%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20as%20she%20argued%20with%20a%20Victoria's%20Secret%20employee%20about%20accepting%20a%20return%20for%20the%20original%20selling%20price%20so%20she%20could%20rebuy%20it%20for%20the%20clearance%20price%3B%20always%20using%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%3Ecredit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20shared%20purchases%20so%20she%20could%20get%20the%20points%20and%20have%20me%20reimburse%20he