ing%20protest%20votes%20for%20third-party%20candidates%20or%20staying%20out%20home%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a07bb1f7-fde3-4a49-8474-a9716bcc12ee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVoter%20apathy%20and%20non-voting%20are%20very%20common%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20never%20had%20an%20election%20where%20voter%20turnout%20is%20100%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20six%20elections%20since%202000%2C%20between%20one-third%20to%20one-half%20of%20eligible%20voters%20have%20failed%20to%20cast%20ballots%2C%20either%20because%20they%20chose%20not%20to%20do%20so%2C%20forgot%20to%20do%20so%2C%20or%20were%20prevented%20from%20doing%20so%20for%20some%20other%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20difficult%20to%20make%20generalizations%20around%20why%20some%20Americans%20don't%20vote%2C%20but%20there%20are%20some%20broad%20theories%20that%20could%20apply.%20One%20theory%20posited%20by%20the%202017%20book%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D4f394eacbfa6a234c7b4def099ea9558a42e2aa7a3cb1a3309e9275038e53e7c%26postID%3D6661bc7eb38735ca9de38bd7%26postSlug%3Dwhy-people-wont-vote-trump-biden-rematch%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAmerican-Nonvoter-Lyn-Ragsdale%252Fdp%252F0190670711%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20Nonvoter%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20a%20sense%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20especially%20driven%20by%20a%20national%20crisis%20such%20as%20a%20pandemic%2C%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20motivating%20less%20engaged%20people%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20election%20presents%20a%20scenario%20that's%20relatively%20rare%3A%20Both%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20have%20been%20president%2C%20they%20have%20both%20been%20fairly%20unpopular%2C%20and%20everyone%20knows%20who%20they%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20almost%20every%20voter%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20the%20most%20recent%20immigrants%20%E2%80%94%20has%20a%20s