n%20Zhang)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A64%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhyundai-palisade-suv-review-my-favorite-cool-features-safety-tech-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Am%20Sorry%20If...%26quot%3B%3A%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Key%20Aide%20VK%20Pandian%20Quits%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20BJD%20suffered%20a%20shock%20defeat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Odisha%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20and%20BJD%20chief%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20key%20aide%20VK%20Pandian%20has%20announced%20that%20he%20is%20quitting%20active%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian%2C%20who%20quit%20the%20civil%20service%20and%20joined%20the%20BJD%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20released%20a%20video%20message%20in%20which%20he%20said%20he%20comes%20from%20a%20humble%20family%20and%20a%20small%20village.%20He%20said%20his%20childhood%20dream%20was%20to%20join%20the%20IAS%20and%20serve%20the%20people.%20%26quot%3B(From)%20the%20day%20I%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20soil%20of%20Odisha%2C%20I%20have%20received%20immense%20love%20and%20affection%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20work%20very%20hard%20for%20the%20people%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian%20said%20it%20has%20been%20an%20honour%20to%20work%20for%20Naveen%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20would%20have%20reached%20the%20milestone%20of%20being%20the%20country's%20longest-serving%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20the%20BJD%20returned%20to%20power.%20%26quot%3BThe%20experience%20and%20learning%20I%20got%20is%20for%20a%20lifetime.%20His%20grace%2C%20leadership%2C%20ethics%20and%20above%20all%2C%20the%20love%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha%20always%20inspired%20me.%20His%20expectation%20from%20me%20was%20to%20implement%20his%20vision%20for%20Odisha%20and%20we%20successfully%20crossed%20many%20milestones%20in%20health%2C%20education%2C%20poverty%20reduction%2C%20ports%2C%20investment%2C%20women%20empowerment%2C%20infrastructure%20and%20also%20in%20temple%20and%20heritage%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian%20said%20he%20left%20the%20IAS%20and%20joined%20the%20BJD%20to%20assist%20his%20mentor%20Naveen%20Patnaik.%20%26quot%3BMy%20only%20intent%20was%20to%20help%20him%2C%20as%20anyone%20would%20do%20for%20his%20mentor%20and%20family.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20set%20straight%20certain%20perceptions%20and%20narratives.%20Perhaps%2C%20it%20has%20been%20my%20shortcoming%20that%20I%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20effectively%20counter%20some%20of%20these%20political%20narratives.%20I%20reiterate%20that%20I%20came%20to%20politics%20to%20help%20my%20mentor%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20ahead%20of%20the%20gruelling%20elections%20and%20I%20had%20no%20desire%2C%20whatsoever%2C%20for%20a%20specific%20political%20post%20or%20power.%20That's%20why%20I%20was%20neither%20a%20candidate%20nor%20was%20I%20holding%20any%20post%20in%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20key%20reasons%20behind%20BJD's%20poor%20show%20in%20this%20election%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Boutsider%26quot%3B%20perception%20about%20Mr%20Pandian%2C%20who%20wielded%20considerable%20clout%20within%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20state's%20administrative%20machinery.%20This%20perception%2C%20further%20stoked%20by%20the%20BJP's%20campaign%2C%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election%20results%20and%20also%20in%20the%20BJD's%20setback%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20BJD%20scored%20a%20blank%20in%20this%20general%20election%2C%20a%20massive%20slide%20from%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2012.%20In%20the%20Assembly%20election%2C%20its%20tally%20was%20down%20from%20112%20seats%20in%202019%20to%2051%20this%20time%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20BJP's%20march%20to%20power.%C2%A0There%20was%20also%20speculation%20that%20Mr%20Pandian%20was%20emerging%20as%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20political%20heir%2C%20a%20buzz%20the%20senior%20leader%20has%20trashed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian%20said%20he%20worked%20hard%20for%2012%20years%20with%20focus%20on%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20and%20Odisha.%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20property%20I%20have%20is%20what%20I%20inherited%20from%20my%20grandparents.%20I%20or%20my%20immediate%20family%20have%20no%20other%20property%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20biggest%20earning%20in%20my%20lifetime%20has%20been%20the%20love%20and%20affection%20and%20goodwill%20of%20people%20of%20Odisha.%20My%20intent%20of%20joining%20politics%20was%20only%20to%20assist%20Naveen%20Babu%20and%20I%20have%20consciously%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20myself%20from%20active%20politics.%20I%20am%20sorry%20if%20I%20have%20hurt%20anyone%20in%20this%20journey.%20I%20am%20sorry%20if%20this%20campaign%20narrative%20against%20me%20has%20had%20a%20part%20to%20play%20in%20BJD's%20loss.%20I%20apologise%20to%20the%20entire%20Biju%20parivar%2C%20including%20all%20workers.%20My%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20lakhs%20of%20Biju%20parivar%20members%20I%20am%20associated%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pandian%20signed%20off%20my%20saying%20that%20he%20will%20always%20pray%20for%20the%20prosperity%20of%20Odisha%20and%20%26quot%3Bmy%20guru%20Naveen%20Patnaik%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik%20defended%20Mr%20Pandian%20against%20the%20criticism%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20poll%20results.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20some%20criticism%20of%20Mr%20Pandian.%20This%20is%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20politician%20said.%20Mr%20Patnaik%20also%20trashed%20rumours%20that%20Mr%20Pandian%20could%20be%20his%20successor.%20%26quot%3BMr%20Pandian%20joined%20the%20party%20but%20has%20not%20had%20any%20posts.%20I%20have%20always%20clearly%20said%20that%20when%20they%20asked%20me%20about%20my%20successor%2C%20I%20said%20clearly%20that%20it%20was%20not%20Mr.%20Pandian.%20I%20repeat%20it.%20The%20people%20of%20Odisha%20will%20decide%20my%20successor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717930620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdv6odpjg_vk-pandian_625x300_07_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-naveen-patnaiks-key-aide-quits-politics-after-shock-odisha-results-5851672%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20BJD%20suffered%20a%20shock%20defeat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Odisha%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20and%20BJD%20chief%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20key%20aide%20VK%20Pandian%20has%20announced%20that%20he%20is%20quitting%20active%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-naveen-patnaiks-key-aide-quits-politics-after-shock-odisha-results-5851672%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-naveen-patnaiks-key-aide-quits-politics-after-shock-odisha-results-5851672%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvk-pandian-naveen-patnaiks-key-aide-quits-politics-after-shock-odisha-results-5851672%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cong%20attacks%20PM%20Modi%20for%20paying%20tribute%20to%20Gandhi%20ahead%20of%20taking%20oath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717930237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110839810%2Cimgsize-2115564.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbreath-taking-hypocrisy-congress-attacks-pm-modi-for-paying-tribute-to-mahatma-gandhi-ahead-of-swearing-in-ceremony%2Farticleshow%2F110839817.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbreath