%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20Melania%20Trump%2C%20and%20Karen%20McDougal.%3Cp%3ELuke%20Hales%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Alon%20Skuy%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Dimitrios%20Kambouris%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Playboy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20prosecutor%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%20criminal%20case%20said%20Melania%20was%20pregnant%20during%20his%20affair%20with%20Karen%20McDougal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20affair%20actually%20began%20after%20Melania%20gave%20birth%20to%20Barron%2C%20two%20sources%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20timeline%20discrepancy%20was%20left%20a%20lingering%20mystery%20after%20the%20trial%20ended%20last%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20criminal%20hush-money%20trial%20has%20given%20the%20public%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstormy-daniels-donald-trump-witness-stand-hush-money-trial-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20details%20than%20anyone%20wanted%20%3C%2Fa%3Eabout%20the%20former%20president's%20sex%20life.%20But%2C%20after%20weeks%20of%20testimony%2C%20one%20mystery%20lingered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20one%20of%20the%20prosecutors%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Trump%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20Karen%20McDougal%2C%20a%20former%20Playboy%20model%2C%20while%20his%20wife%2C%20Melania%20Trump%2C%20was%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20that%20McDougal%20and%20Trump%20had%20an%20affair%20was%20not%20new.%20The%20idea%20that%20the%20affair%20took%20place%20while%20Melania%20Trump%20was%20expecting%20a%20child%2C%20however%2C%20had%20never%20been%20previously%20reported.%20The%20prosecutor%2C%20Assistant%20District%20Attorney%20Joshua%20Steinglass%2C%20disclosed%20it%20at%20a%20hearing%20just%20before%20jury%20selection%20began%2C%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20April%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20was%20that%20detail%20that%20would%20bolster%20the%20prosecution's%20argument%20that%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-hush-money-trial-charges-explained-narrative-as-jury-deliberates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilenced%20women%20to%20benefit%20his%202016%20presidential%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20this%20relationship%20occurred%20during%20the%20defendant's%20wife's%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20child%2C%20speaks%20directly%20to%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20defendant%20believed%20the%20story%20would%20be%20damaging%20to%20his%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinglass%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20two%20sources%20with%20knowledge%20of%20McDougal's%20relationship%20with%20Trump%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20got%20the%20detail%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20just%20as%20surprised%20as%20you%20when%20Josh%20Steinglass%20stated%20that%20Melania%20was%20pregnant%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Carol%20Heller%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20McDougal%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20trysts%20between%20Trump%20and%20McDougal%2C%20and%20who%20testified%20in%20the%20trial%2C%20confirmed%20the%20relationship%20began%20%26quot%3Bsoon%20after%20the%20birth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinglass%20dropped%20the%20apparent%20bombshell%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20journalists%20flooded%20the%20chilly%20Manhattan%20courtroom%20for%20the%20trial%2C%20before%20a%20single%20juror%20had%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20the%20judge%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-judge-juan-merchan-manhattan-mental-health-court-wednesday-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20allow%20McDougal%20to%20testify%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKaren%20McDougal%20is%20a%20former%20Playboy%20model%20who%20claimed%20to%20have%20had%20a%20romantic%20and%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20Mr.%20Trump%20that%20lasted%20nearly%20a%20year%2C%20including%20while%20Mr.%20Trump's%20wife%2C%20Melania%2C%20was%20pregnant%20with%20their%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20District%20Attorney%20Steinglass%20told%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20something%20didn't%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20previous%20media%20interviews%2C%20McDougal%20said%20the%20affair%20spanned%2010%20months%2C%20beginning%20around%20Trump's%20birthday%20in%20June%202006%20and%20lasting%20until%20April%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarron%20Trump%2C%20the%20sole%20child%20of%20Donald%20and%20Melania%20Trump%2C%20was%20born%20in%20March%202006%20%E2%80%94%20before%20McDougal%20says%20the%20affair%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222007%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Karen%20Mcdougal%202007%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66636f68e079049018172902%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKaren%20McDougal%20at%20a%20Playboy%20golf%20event%20in%202007%2C%20during%20the%20time%20she%20says%20she%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20Trump.%3Cp%3EChad%20Buchanan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Heller%2C%20Merchan%20relied%20on%20Steinglass's%20error%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-judge-melania-pregnant-testimony-playboy-model-affair-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20ruled%20prosecutors%20should%20not%20question%20McDougal%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20subject%20on%20the%20witness%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteinglass%20had%20told%20the%20judge%20he%20would%20not%20elicit%20%26quot%3Bthe%20salacious%20details%20of%20the%20affair%2C%20to%20describe%20the%20sexual%20acts%20or%20locales%20of%20their%20liaisons%26quot%3B%20from%20McDougal%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20Trump's%20lawyers%20would%20%26quot%3Bopen%20the%20door%26quot%3B%20to%20it.%20Bu