-da-evidence-against-his-client-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20marathon%20five-hour%20closing%20argument%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-hush-money-trial-verdict-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejury%20convicted%20Trump%20of%20all%2034%20counts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cc2c7c15-c00d-4781-bf91-6162039dc149%5C%22%3EMcDougal's%20story%20helped%20explain%20'catch%20and%20kill'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Trump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nydailynews.com%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2Fpresident-trump-used-to-boast-about-having-sex-with-his-friends-wives-devised-calculated-infidelity-plots%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboasted%20about%20his%20infidelity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20general%20terms%2C%20but%20has%20seldom%20publicly%20talked%20about%20McDougal%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20April%20court%20hearing%2C%20Trump's%20lead%20defense%20attorney%2C%20Todd%20Blanche%2C%20called%20McDougal's%20story%20%26quot%3Bunproven%26quot%3B%20but%20did%20not%20discuss%20the%20details%20of%20her%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Blanche%20nor%20representatives%20for%20Melania%20Trump%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUntil%20Mr.%20Trump%20himself%20confirms%20their%20affair%2C%20or%20until%20any%20witness%20in%20whom%20he%20has%20previously%20confided%20comes%20forward%20to%20verify%20his%20admission%2C%20I%20suppose%20Mr.%20Blanche%20can%20legally%20describe%20their%20affair%20as%20'unproven%2C'%26quot%3B%20Heller%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BKaren%20will%20always%20hold%20it%20as%20the%20truth%2C%20because%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniels%20received%20%24130%2C000%20in%20hush%20money%20in%20October%202016.%20The%20alleged%20affair%20with%20McDougal%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20an%20earlier%20hush-money%20arrangement%2C%20in%20June%20of%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3