nated%20from%20a%20text%20message%20from%20Gina%20Rodriquez%2C%20a%20talent%20agent%20who%20previously%20represented%20Daniels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20October%202016%20text%20message%20to%20Dylan%20Howard%2C%20who%20then%20served%20as%20the%20editor-in-chief%20of%20the%20National%20Enquirer%2C%20Rodriguez%20said%20Daniels%20would%20%26quot%3Btake%20a%20lie%20detector%20and%20go%20on%20the%20record%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20affair%20taking%20place%20while%20Melania%20was%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20had%20sex%20with%20Stormy%20Daniels%20while%20his%20current%20wife%20was%20pregnant%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodriguez%20wrote%20in%20the%20text%20message.%20%26quot%3BHe%20flew%20Stormy%20to%20his%20Pageant%20and%20told%20her%20he%20would%20get%20her%20on%20Celebrity%20Apprentice%20which%20he%20never%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20be%20true%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20trial%20testimony%20from%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20she%20met%20Trump%20at%20a%20Lake%20Tahoe%20celebrity%20golf%20tournament%20in%20July%20of%202006%20%E2%80%94%20months%20after%20Barron%20Trump%20was%20born.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERodriguez%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20evidence%20photo%20from%20Donald%20Trump's%20NY%20hush-money%20trial%20showing%20him%20with%20his%20arm%20around%20Stormy%20Daniels%20during%20a%202006%20celebrity%20golf%20tournament%20in%20Lake%20Tahoe.%20Daniels%20says%20this%20picture%20was%20taken%20hours%20before%20they%20had%20sex%20in%20his%20hotel%20suite.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666370a6ed9a404d829be077%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20photo%20from%20a%202006%20celebrity%20golf%20tournament%20in%20Lake%20Tahoe%20was%20taken%20hours%20before%20Stormy%20Daniels%20says%20she%20had%20sex%20with%20Donald%20Trump.%3Cp%3EManhattan