0cheque%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cheque%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20criminals%20used%20to%20send%20Rs%2085%20lakh%20to%20105%20accounts%20across%20India%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20cheque%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20criminals%20used%20to%20send%20Rs%2085%20lakh%20to%20105%20accounts%20across%20India%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fa93qr068_rana-garments-cheque_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cheque%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20company%20in%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20criminals%20used%20to%20send%20Rs%2085%20lakh%20to%20105%20accounts%20across%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Crime%20Branch%20has%20taken%20several%20documents%20from%20the%20HDFC%20Bank%20branch%20in%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20bank%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20case%20when%20he%20met%20the%20bank%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHDFC%20Bank%20said%20they%20are%20cooperating%20with%20the%20Crime%20Branch.%20I%20have%20also%20told%20the%20police%2C%20was%20no%20KYC%20(know%20your%20customer)%20done%20for%20Rana%20Garments%20by%20the%20Uttam%20Nagar%20(Delhi)%20branch%3F%20The%20police%20in%20Delhi%20went%20to%20Rana%20Garments%20and%20found%20the%20place%20was%20occupied%20by%20another%20company.%20The%20Rana%20Garments%20owner%20is%20untraceable%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20retired%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20after%20the%20retirement%20savings%20got%20credited%20into%20the%20officer's%20HDFC%20Bank%20account%2C%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20man%20who%20identified%20himself%20as%20%26quot%3BDCP%20Cyber%20Crime%20Balsing%20Rajput%26quot%3B.%20He%20told%20the%20retired%20officer%20his%20name%20has%20come%20up%20on%20several%20narcotics%20and%20money%20laundering%20cases%20and%20