ld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistans-fifth-polio-case-raises-concerns-over-surveillance-lapses%2Farticleshow%2F110835377.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110835377.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20confirmation%20of%20the%20fifth%20polio%20case%20this%20year%20in%20Quetta%2C%20Balochistan%20has%20sparked%20concerns%20about%20surveillance%20lapses.%20The%20potential%20for%20increased%20transmission%20comes%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%20in%20the%20polio%20eradication%20campaign%2C%20reports%20Dawn.%20The%20case%2C%20reported%20on%20April%2029%20and%20confirmed%20on%20June%208%2C%20underscores%20a%20significant%20six-week%20delay%20in%20diagnosis.%20This%20points%20to%20a%20notable%20gap%20in%20identifying%20and%20addressing%20poliovirus%20infections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistans-fifth-polio-case-raises-concerns-over-surveillance-lapses%2Farticleshow%2F110835377.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistans-fifth-polio-case-raises-concerns-over-surveillance-lapses%2Famp_articleshow%2F110835377.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistans-fifth-polio-case-raises-concerns-over-surveillance-lapses%2Famp_articleshow%2F110835377.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Modi%203.0%3A%20Continuity%20At%20The%20Top%20Will%20Add%20Heft%20To%20India's%20Foreign%20Policy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6dikd448_pm-modi_625x300_07_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20domestic%20politics%2C%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20secure%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20own%20in%20the%20just-concluded%20national%20elections%20in%20India%20is%20undoubtedly%20a%20setback.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20personally%20confident%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20get%20an%20absolute%20majority%20on%20its%20own%20and%20could%20touch%20the%20400%20mark%20with%20its%20alliance%20partners.%20The%20BJP%20has%20secured%20240%20seats%20(compared%20to%20303%20in%202019)%20and%20293%20in%20total%20with%20its%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20led%20by%20Modi%20will%20now%20form%20the%20next%20government.%20Securing%20a%20third%20term%20as%20leader%20is%20an%20exceptional%20feat%20in%20a%20Western-style%20democracy.%20Anti-incumbency%2C%20a%20desire%20for%20change%2C%20and%20loss%20of%20public%20appeal%20after%20a%20long%20tenure%20affect%20politicians%20in%20a%20democratic%20set-up.%20In%20%C2%A0India%2C%20Nehru%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20three%20times%20but%20no%20Prime%20Minister%20after%201962%20has%20secured%20three%20terms.%20Internationally%2C%20in%20Western-style%20democracies%2C%20only%20six%20political%20leaders%20(Nehru%20included)%20have%20succeeded%20in%20winning%20three%20electoral%20mandates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird-Term%20Objectives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20had%20announced%20during%20his%20election%20campaign%20the%20goals%20for%20his%20third%20term%2C%20the%20principal%20being%20that%20of%20making%20India%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20economy%20by%202029.%20For%20achieving%20that%2C%20his%20list%20includes%20economic%20and%20bureaucratic%20reforms%2C%20attracting%20foreign%20investment%20and%20global%20supply%20chains%20to%20India%2C%20increasing%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20building%20an%20advanced%20technology%20base%20including%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20semiconductors%20and%20electronics%2C%20becoming%20more%20self-reliant%20in%20defence%20manufacturing%20and%20expanding%20defence%20exports%2C%20greater%20digitalisation%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20expanding%20India's%20soft%20power%20based%20on%20its%20civilisational%20attributes.%20The%20overarching%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20economy%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20policy%20was%20not%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20elections.%20Some%20indication%20of%20the%20NDA's%20thinking%20on%20foreign%20policy%20issues%20was%20available%20from%20its%20manifesto.%20India's%20leadership%20and%20presence%20in%20global%20forums%2C%20including%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20chaired%20by%20India%20figured%20in%20it.%20The%20Neighbourhood%20First%20policy%20was%20reiterated.%20No%20mention%20was%20made%20specifically%20of%20the%20US%2C%20but%20collaboration%20with%20countries%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20was%20mentioned%2C%20with%20growth%20and%20security%20for%20all%20as%20a%20goal.%20China%20too%20was%20not%20mentioned%2C%20but%20accelerating%20the%20development%20of%20infrastructure%20on%20the%20India-China%20border%20was.%20Support%20for%20Israel%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20terrorism%2C%20India's%20aspiration%20for%20permanent%20membership%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20figured%20in%20the%20manifesto.%20Substantial%20gains%20in%20the%20global%20spread%20of%20India's%20soft%20power%20such%20as%20the%20International%20Yoga%20Day%20and%20Ayurveda%20found%20mention.%20The%20return%20of%20stolen%20artefacts%20to%20the%20country%20and%20encouraging%20the%20study%20of%20Indian%20classical%20languages%20in%20educational%20institutions%20across%20the%20world%20were%20the%20other%20subjects%20included%20in%20the%20manifesto.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERenewed%20Engagement%20with%20Russia%20likely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20Modi%20did%20not%20dwell%20on%20foreign%20policy%20issues.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20a%20Western%20media%20outlet%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20importance%20of%20India-China%20relations%20but%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20normalise%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20border.%20He%20spoke%20of%20India's%20vocation%20of%20being%20friends%20with%20all%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20besides%20increasing%20its%20role%20in%20world%20affairs.%20The%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20however%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20audiences%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20India%20to%20familiarise%20them%20with%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20India's%20foreign%20policy.%20The%20Minister%20has%20been%20stoutly%20defending%20India's%20ties%20with%20Russia%2C%20its%20attachment%20to%20multi-alignment%2C%20the%20importance%20attached%20to%20Quad%2C%20and%20the%20absolute%20need%20to%20normalise%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20India-China%20border%20as%20that%20alone%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20normalisation%20of%20bilateral%20ties.%20The%20Minister%20has%20also%20been%20exposing%20with%20unusual%20frankness%20the%20double%20standards%20of%20the%20West%20on%20many%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20had%2C%20with%20the%20force%20of%20his%20personality%2C%20his%20self-assurance%2C%20his%20pursuit%20of%20an%20independent%20foreign%20policy%2C%20a%20sharp%20focus%20on%20national%20interest%20and%20an%20ability%20to%20build%20good%20personal%20rapport%20with%20foreign%20leaders%2C%20put%20his%20stamp%20on%20the%20international%20scene.%20The%20growth%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20during%20his%20tenure%20added%20strength%20to%20his%20handling%20of%20India's%20diplomatic%20options.%20The%20success%20of%20India's%20G-20%20presidency%20under%20his%20leadership%20contributed%20to%20raising%20his%20international%20stature.%20It%20was%20widely%20believed%20that%20he%20would%20win%20his%20third%20term%20easily.%20The%20electoral%20rebuff%20that%20he%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20received%20has%20raised%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20this%20will%20now%20affect%20the%20%C3%A9lan%20of%20his%20leadership%20at%20the%20global%20level%20and%20aspects%20of%20India's%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20did%20the%20opposition%20in%20India%2C%20legitimately%20in%20terms%20of%20domestic%20politics%2C%20pull%20out%20all%20stops%20to%20deny%20Modi%20a%20third%20term%20victory%2C%20but%20international%20lobbies%20have%20illegitimately%20interfered%20in%20India's%20domestic%20politics.%20And%20this%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20to%20deny%20the%20BJP%20a%20single%20party%20majority%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20weakening%20Modi%20internally%20and%20externally%2C%20and%20have%20leverages%20to%20make%20India%20more%20amenable%20to%20Western%20persuasion%20and%20pressure.%20India's%20rise%20inevitably%20means%20accelerating%20the%20shift%20of%20power%20from%20the%20West%20to%20the%20East.%20The%20rise%20of%20a%20power%20that%20seeks%20multipolarity%2C%20eschews%20alliances%20and%20seeks%20a%20greater%20role%20in%20international%20governance%20cannot%20but%20affect%20the%20strategic%20calculations%20of%20established%20powers%20on%20handling%20the%20global%20system%20in%20ways%20that%20allow%20them%20to%20safeguard%20their%20traditional%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20a%20confluence%20of%20opposition%20political%20forces%20in%20India%20and%20anti-Modi%20lobbies%20in%20the%20West%20has%20sought%20to%20make%20the%20task%20of%20governing%20India%20as%20per%20the%20BJP's%20agenda%20as%20difficult%20as%20possible.%20One%20of%20the%20tools%20for%20this%20has%20been%20tarnishing%20India's%20image%20by%20raising%20concerns%20about%20deficits%20on%20issues%20of%20democracy%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20treatment%20of%20minorities%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeaching%20Anti-India%20Elements%20A%20Lesson%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%202024%20election%2C%20western%20media%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20foundations%2C%20human%20rights%20organisations%20and%20academics%20launched%20what%20seemed%20an%20orchestrated%20campaign%20against%20the%20Modi%20government.%20This%20campaign%20has%20closely%20mirrored%20the%20accusations%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20and%20sundry%20civil%20society%20organisations%20in%20India%20about%20negative%20developments%20in%20the%20country.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ELe%20Monde%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeutsche%20Welle%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20etc%2C%20have%20been%20effectively%20playing%20politics%20through%20their%20heavily%20slanted%20reports.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Economist%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%2C%20unsurprisingly%2C%20welcomed%20the%20%26quot%3Bhumbling%26quot%3B%20of%20Modi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20Western%20media%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20foundations%2C%20academics%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%20have%20spearheaded%20the%20campaign%20against%20Modi%2C%20it%20is%20with%20the%20active%20or%20tacit%20encouragement%20of%20what%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Deep%20State%2C%20namely%2C%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%2C%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20political%20lobbies.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20publishes%20reports%20on%20human%20rights%20and%20religious%20freedoms%20in%20India%20and%20comments%20on%20even%20minor%20communal%20incidents%20in%20a%20country%20as%20vast%20and%20populous%20as%20India%20shows%20the%20feedback%20loops%20that%20operate.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20not%20news%20for%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20India%20has%20to%20find%20a%20balance%20in%20its%20larger%20national%20interest%20between%20the%20productive%20and%20the%20more%20problematic%20parts%20of%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20West.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20third-term%20Modi%20government%20to%20decide%20what%20it%20should%20do%20to%20discipline%20%5C%5Cforeign%20journalists%20in%20India%20whose%20bias%20against%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20and%20interference%20in%20our%20internal%20politics%20have%20been%20manifest.%20%C2%A0Maybe%20the%20time%20has%20come%20to%20bite%20the%20bullet%20and%20think%20of%20cancelling%20the%20accreditation%20of%20the%20most%20egregious%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELittle%20Change%20In%20Policy%20Direction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20after%20the%20election%20results%2C%20Modi%20made%20it%20amply%20clear%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20direction%20and%20content%20of%20the%20policies%20that%20he%20had%20already%20broadly%20defined%20for%20his%20third%20term.%20In%20the%20area%20of%20foreign%20policy%2C%20there%20is%20no%20compulsion%20whatsoever%20to%20change%20course.%20Efforts%20to%20cultivate%20the%20neighbours%20will%20continue%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20China%20challenge%20becoming%20more%20daunting.%20China%20will%20be%20countered%20on%20the%20border%20and%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20even%20as%20the%20doors%20of%20dialogue%20are%20kept%20open%20and%20economic%20ties%20are%20only%20selectively%20reduced.%20Relations%20with%20Russia%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20given%20due%20importance%2C%20the%20potential%20of%20their%20expansion%20will%20be%20explored%20and%20the%20summit-level%20dialogue%20with%20Russia%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20resumed.%20The%20geopolitical%20advantages%20of%20our%20membership%20of%20BRICS%20and%20the%20SCO%20will%20continue.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnCooperation%20in%20various%20domains%20with%20the%20US%20is%20vital%20for%20our%20future%20growth%20and%20technological%20progress%20will%20continue%20to%20expand%20pragmatically.%20%C2%A0The%20Quad%20agenda%20will%20be%20pursued%2C%20ties%20with%20the%20Gulf%20countries%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20reinforced%2C%20and%20amplifying%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20internationally%20will%20remain%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20our%20effort%20to%20expand%20our%20own%20global%20role%20and%20influence.%20The%20global%20spread%20of%20India's%20soft%20power%20flowing%20from%20its%20civilisational%20legacies%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20an%20important%20foreign%20policy%20objective.%20The%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Evishwabandhu%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20in%20a%20sense%20signifies%20independence%20in%20foreign%20policy%20making%2C%20multi-alignment%20and%20not%20getting%20involved%20in%20third-party%20conflicts%2C%20will%20be%20the%20broad%20feature%20of%20our%20foreign%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20important%20in%20the%20international%20context%20is%20Modi's%20continuance%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20Whether%20he%20got%20an%20absolute%20majority%20in%20the%20elections%20or%20not%20is%20not%20very%20relevant%20in%20foreign%20dealings.%20Many%20leaders%20in%20the%20West%20have%20either%20not%20won%20majorities%20or%20their%20popularity%20has%20dipped%20drastically%20after%20elections%2C%20or%20they%20are%20leaders%20of%20coalition%20governments.%20The%20world%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20leaders%20in%20power.%20Whether%20India%20will%20have%20a%20stable%20government%20and%20therefore%20stable%20policies%20is%20of%20greater%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaging%20domestic%20politics%20in%20India%20with%20all%20its%20diversities%20and%20fractures%20was%20already%20difficult%20even%20with%20the%20BJP%20having%20an%20absolute%20majority%20in%20the%20first%20two%20terms.%20The%20BJP's%20reduced%20majority%20will%20encourage%20opposition%20elements%20to%20become%20more%20raucous.%20They%20will%20also%20try%20to%20leverage%20foreign%20anti-Indian%20lobbies%2C%20as%20before%2C%20to%20generate%20pressure%20on%20the%20government.%20A%20stronger%20pushback%20from%20the%20government%20against%20foreign%20interference%20will%20be%20necessary%20to%20discourage%20this.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20coalition%20government%20this%20time%2C%20however%2C%20is%20much%20stronger%20and%20more%20stable%20than%20what%20has%20been%20the%20case%20between%20the%201990s%20and%202014.%20The%20economic%20outlook%20of%20India%20remains%20bright%20because%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20the%20economy%20are%20strong.%20The%20lure%20of%20India%20for%20the%20West%20is%20not%20its%20democracy%20but%20its%20growing%20economy%2C%20its%20expanding%20market%20and%20its%20human%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717921260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F6dikd448_pm-modi_625x300_07_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcontinuity-at-the-top-will-add-heft-to-indias-foreign-policy-5851132%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20leaders%20in%20power.%20Whether%20India%20will%20have%20a%20stable%20government%20and%20therefore%20stable%20policies%20is%20of%20greater%20importance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcontinuity-at-the-top-will-add-heft-to-indias-foreign-policy-5851132%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Mexico%20heat%20wave%20monkeys%20still%20dying%2C%20birds%20are%20getting%20air-conditioning%2C%20lions%20get%20popsicles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717921063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110835241%2Cimgsize-1025983.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofi