edia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-03-at-18.45.33-min-1717420586-1024x1536.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-03-at-18.45.33-min-1717420586-150x225.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-03-at-18.45.33-min-1717420586.jpeg%201067w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGagan%20Anand%2C%20Founder%2C%20Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20business%20idea%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20something%20in%20ice-cream%20%E2%80%93%20but%20with%20a%20twist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%20September%202020%2C%20%E2%80%98Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20dessert%20cafe%2C%20serves%20%E2%80%98live%E2%80%99%20popsicles%20and%20gelato.%20Over%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20the%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20having%20over%2030%20stores%20across%20the%20country%20with%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%208%20crores%20in%20the%20last%20financial%20year%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20not%20having%20money%20to%20afford%20rent%20to%20providing%20employment%20to%20over%20140%20people%20today%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20Gagan%E2%80%99s%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBig%20dreams%2C%20humble%20beginnings%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGagan%E2%80%99s%20father%20worked%20as%20a%20block%20agriculture%20officer%20which%20meant%20frequent%20transfers%20and%20postings%20in%20rural%20Bihar%2FJharkhand%20where%20electricity%20was%20a%20luxury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20