20have%20now%20understood%20is%20that%20there%20is%20always%20a%20male%20and%20a%20female%20flower%20in%20the%20plant.%20So%2C%20even%20while%20the%20fruit%20is%20being%20borne%20on%20the%20female%20flower%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20male%20flower%20for%20pollination%20to%20occur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-500x879.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Sharma%20has%20cultivated%20a%20thriving%20terrace%20garden%20in%20his%20Delhi%20apartment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-500x879.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-171x300.jpeg%20171w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-768x1350.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-874x1536.jpeg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-150x264.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739.jpeg%20910w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350879%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMayank%20Sharma%20has%20cultivated%20a%20thriving%20terrace%20garden%20in%20his%20Delhi%20apartment%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Mayank%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this