20pieces%20and%20not%20pounded%20to%20be%20properly%20mixed.%20When%20you%20use%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20actually%20blending%20all%20the%20oils%20of%20the%20herbs%20and%20spices%20together%20to%20enhance%20the%20flavours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20was%20determined%20to%20revive%20the%20traditional%20practice%20of%20using%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20With%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%20160%2C%20he%20bought%20the%20grinding%20stone%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20fresh%20coriander%2C%20and%20green%20chillies%2C%20and%20kicked%20off%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pisyun%20loon%20is%20a%20pahadi%20salt%20which%20is%20prepared%20by%20hand%20grounding%20spices%20and%20herbs%20on%20silbatta%20(traditional%20grinding%20stone).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FHimFla-1-1716968093-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351422%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPisyun%20loon%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20%3Cem%3Epahadi%20%3C%2Fem%3Esalt%20prepared%20by%20hand%20grounding%20spices%20and%20herbs%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Esilbatta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(traditional%20grinding%20stone).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3